`--api-type-document-child-docs-margin-left` | Margin left of the item's properties description relative to the title when the item is a child property of another property | `24px`

`--api-type-document-type-background-color` | Background color of the "type" trait | `#2196F3`

properties.name: type
properties.description:
A type definition to render.
This should be a one of the following AMF types:

- `http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#NodeShape` (Object)
- `http://raml.org/vocabularies/shapes#UnionShape` (Union)
- `http://raml.org/vocabularies/shapes#ArrayShape` (Array)
- `http://raml.org/vocabularies/shapes#ScalarShape` (single property)

It also accepts array of properties like list of headers or
parameters.

properties.name: parentTypeName

Should be set if described properties has a parent type.
This is used when recursively iterating over properties.

properties.description: True if given `type` is a scalar property

properties.name: isArray
properties.description: True if given `type` is an array property

properties.name: isObject
properties.description: True if given `type` is an object property

properties.name: isUnion
properties.description: True if given `type` is an union property

properties.name: unionTypes
properties.description:
Computed list of union type types to render in union type
selector.
Each item has `label` and `isScalar` property.

properties.name: selectedUnion
properties.description: Selected index of union type in `unionTypes` array.

elements.name: ApiElements.ApiTypeDocument

attributes.name: amf-model
attributes.description:
Generated AMF json/ld model form the API spec.
The element assumes the object of the first array item to be a
type of `"http://raml.org/vocabularies/document#Document`
on AMF vocabulary.

It is only usefult for the element to resolve references.

attributes.name: shape
attributes.description: A property shape definition of AMF.

attributes.name: range
attributes.description: Computes value of shape's http://raml.org/vocabularies/shapes#range

attributes.name: aware
attributes.description: `raml-aware` scope property to use.

attributes.name: type
attributes.description:
A type definition to render.
This should be a one of the following AMF types:

- `http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#NodeShape` (Object)
- `http://raml.org/vocabularies/shapes#UnionShape` (Union)
- `http://raml.org/vocabularies/shapes#ArrayShape` (Array)
- `http://raml.org/vocabularies/shapes#ScalarShape` (single property)

It also accepts array of properties like list of headers or
parameters.

attributes.name: parent-type-name
attributes.description:
Should be set if described properties has a parent type.
This is used when recursively iterating over properties.

attributes.name: is-scalar
attributes.description: True if given `type` is a scalar property

attributes.name: is-array
attributes.description: True if given `type` is an array property

attributes.name: is-object
attributes.description: True if given `type` is an object property

attributes.name: is-union
attributes.description: True if given `type` is an union property

attributes.name: union-types
attributes.description:
Computed list of union type types to render in union type
selector.
Each item has `label` and `isScalar` property.

attributes.name: selected-union
attributes.description: Selected index of union type in `unionTypes` array.
